== Zend Framework Model Mappers for GitHub's API ==
A best practice example of how to use zf mappers with a webservice. Unit tests & mocks included. 

Any suggestions / ideas / improvememts welcome...


== Example usage ==
$registry = Zend_Registry::getInstance();
$datasource = new Github_Model_Datasource($registry);
$model = new Github_Model_Mapper_Repo($datasource)
$result = $model->findByUsername(new Github_Model_User(array('username' => $username)));

== Example Mock usage ==
$mock = new Github_Test_Model_Mock;
$model = new Github_Model_Mapper_Repo($mock)
$result = $model->findByUsername(new Github_Model_User(array('username' => $username)));

== Example run unit tests ==
> cd /tests
> phpunit
